      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9]{Theorem (Ex)}</p>\n<p>As a reaction, when an ally within the first range increment of an injection weapon you’re wielding would fall unconscious from damage, you can spend 2 Resolve Points to render instant emergency medical aid to that ally, preventing any excess damage that would reduce them below 0 and restoring Hit Points to them equal to your level. A creature can’t be affected by this ability more than once per 24 hours.</p>"
